TOTh 2016 Training session
"The contribution of Linguistics to Terminology"
7 & 8 June 2016
Université Savoie Mont Blanc – Campus Scientifique – Le Bourget du Lac
(Chambéry France)
http://www.porphyre.org/toth

The TOTh training sessions are organised over two days immediately
before the TOTh Conference. They aim to promote collaboration among
language and knowledge professionals. The 2016 TOTh training session
will focus on ‘The contribution of Linguistics to Terminology’, the
2017 training session on ‘The contribution of Ontology to
Terminology’.

Registration form: http://www.porphyre.org/toth-registration/
